@node "WHAT" "What Is Final Typer ?"


WHAT IS FINAL TYPER?
--------------------
Final Typer is a very small program which allows you to type into your texts
also those so strange chars that are present in foreing languages. It is a
better solution than learning mad-driven ALT-sequences.



@endnode

@node "NEED" "What You Need"


WHAT YOU NEED
-------------
- One (or more... ;) Amiga
- Final Writer 3 (earlier version may not work :( )
- Final Writer MUST open into a CUSTOM Screen!!!

@endnode

@node "INSTALL" "Installation"

INSTALLATION
------------
To install Final Typer is not very simple, but neither so difficult.
Follow all these steps and you will be a very happy user of Final Typer.

    1 - Copy "FinalTyper" file inside the dir you wish to hold it.
    2 - Edit file "CallFinalTyper" and insert the correct path where
        FinalTyper should be found by Final Writer and save it.
    3 - Copy edited "CallFinalTyper" file inside FinalWriter/FWMacros
        directory.
    4 - Load FinalWriter and choose "Preferences/User Menu" from the
        "Project" Menu. A window will pop up.
    5 - Press "New" Gadget into the Actions section.
    6 - Insert "Final Typer" into "Menu Item Name" String gadget.
    7 - Select "ARexx Script" into "Command Definition" section.
    8 - Click on "Select..." into "Command" section and select "CallFinalTyper"
        into FinalWriter/FWMacros directory or wherelse you copy it.
    9 - Press the "SAVE" button.

    YOU GOT IT!!!! FinalTyper is Installed.

@endnode

@node WHATSNEW "What's New"
Final Typer V2.00 has been completely rewritten. There are SO MANY users
I feel the need to write a new version of this great program.
Well... my efforts took me here: so far, so good.

New features:

        * Multi Window
          Now Final Typer does not tie the user to use just ONE single
          window of chars per time... now you can have also ALL chars
          windows opened at the same time!!!

        * Font sensitive
          now FinalTyper uses your FW default font! So Final Typer has the
          same Final Writer look!

        * Resizable interface
          You can size the interface as you like.

        * Shorter code
          Final Typer has been completely rewritten. Now the code is
          in Amiga E and it is more compact and useful. It requires
          also less memory to execute!

        * More System Friendly
          Now Final Typer is more system friendly than ever!
          No enforcer's hits... just the screen grabbing routine is
          not _really_ system friendly ;)

        * Final Writer V4 TESTED!
          This version of Final Typer has been tested also on FW4... and it
          works properely.

        * Library free (!!!)
          Even if the interface is font sensitive and resizable, you do not
          need to load any interface-library such as MUI/BGUI and so on!

        * Faster
          Final Typer is faster than its predecessor, thanks to its completely
          rewritten structure.

        * More Expandible
          Now Final Typer is modular. If you wish to have some chars added to
          the list, drop me a mail, and I will do it!

        * Free
          Final Typer is still Free Ware! You can use it without giving me
          any buck! But, please, send me an e-mail! ;)

 *** If you have liked Final Typer V1.00 you will LOVE this new version! ***


V2.50   - Now completely ARexx-ware: I do not write a temp rexx file into
          Ram:T, but just talk with FinalWriter through ARexx.

        - X Chars window has been improved. Thanks to Richard Knight for
          his suggestions.

        - Now FinalTyper is e-mail ware: send me a mail if you use it!
@endnode

